DR001

STATEMENT all chat messages since the start of the conference shall be viewable, even by users who joined after those messaged were sent
PRIORITY A

STATEMENT a moderator shall be able to clear the whiteboard
PRIORIY A

STATMENET in  document sharing, each user can save his own version (snapshot) of the document being worked on.
PRIORITY A

STATEMENT All records, saved on the server, shall be accessable by the participating members.
PRIORITY A

STATEMENT All records, saved on the server, shall be downloadable.
PRIORITY A

STATEMENT in document sharing, only one user can edit the document at one time. The moderator or a sub-moderator can switch the write access between users
PRIORITY B
